*[[Toxic blowpipe]] (to kill minions)
*[[Serpentine helm]] (to envenom minions at start of kill) (optional)
*[[Venator bow]] (to kill minions while stacked and/or as a Zarosian item, optional)
*[[Ecumenical key]] (optional)
*Any required god items, with one Saradomin and one Zamorak item being strongly recommended, and optionally a Zarosian item if banking at the [[Ancient Prison]]
*1-4 [[stamina potion]]s (optional for higher levelled and geared players, or those using run energy neutral kiting methods)
*8-16 [[Saradomin brew]]s or [[sharks]] (brews & super restores should be brought in a 3:1 ratio)
*6-12 [[super restore]]s or [[prayer potion]]s
*1-4 [[Divine bastion potion|divine bastion potions]] or [[Divine ranging potion]]s
*[[Explorer's ring 4]] for access to [[High level alchemy]] regardless of spellbook and run energy restoration
*A [[divine rune pouch]] containing [[law runes]], [[nature runes]], [[dust runes]] and [[steam runes]] will allow the player to cast [[Trollheim teleport]], [[Teleport to house]], [[High level alchemy]] and [[Bones to peaches]]
*[[Ghommal's hilt]] or two [[Trollheim teleport tablet]]s. Revert one to a [[Teleport to house (tablet)]] once you arrive.
*Alternatively, a [[book of the dead]] with a rune pouch containing [[fire runes]], [[blood runes]], and [[cosmic runes]] for [[resurrection spells]].
*[[Armadyl brews]] can be used in place of [[Saradomin brews]] with a more advanced method involving [[Menaphite remedies]] to restore lowered [[defence]] levels; [[defence]] levels lost are restored by the remedy every 15 seconds. 
**This has the benefit of keeping your [[Divine ranging]] [[boost]] and also requiring one less sipping action when healing via [[Armadyl brews]] when done correctly. 
***e.g. [[Menaphite remedy]] -> [[Divine ranging]] -> 2x [[Armadyl brew]] sips per 15 seconds to maintain a decent [[defence]] level while also not cancelling the divine status.
**This comes with a caveat that you must have sufficient [[equipment]] with high [[ranged]] [[defence]] as [[Bree]] has a low max hit, but will be very consistent on your lower, unboosted defence.
***Due to this, Consider bringing [[Super restores]] instead of [[Prayer potions]] with this method as consecutively drinking [[Armadyl brews]] may lower defence too much for the [[Menaphite remedy]] to restore defence in a timely manner, negating any health gained.
